LICENSING NOTICE FOR GO-SEND
============================

This project uses a dual-licensing approach:

1. GO BACKEND (GPL-3.0)
   All Go source code in this repository (excluding views/) is licensed
   under the GNU General Public License version 3.0.

2. FRONTEND (MIXED LICENSING)
   The frontend in views/ contains files under two licenses:

   a) MPL-2.0 Licensed Files (from original Firefox Send):
      - views/src/api.mjs
      - views/src/archive.mjs
      - views/src/ece.mjs
      - views/src/fileReceiver.mjs
      - views/src/fileSender.mjs
      - views/src/keychain.mjs
      - views/src/ownedFile.mjs
      - views/src/streams.mjs
      - views/src/zip.mjs

      These files are derived from Mozilla's Firefox Send and are
      licensed under the Mozilla Public License 2.0.
      See LICENSE.MPL-2.0 for the full license text.

   b) GPL-3.0 Licensed Files (new implementation):
      All other files in views/, including:
      - All UI components (views/src/ui/*)
      - Controller and routing (views/src/controller.mjs, views/src/main.mjs)
      - Templates (views/templates/*)
      - Build configuration

For detailed licensing information, see:
- LICENSE.MPL-2.0 (Mozilla Public License 2.0 full text)
- views/src/LICENSE (detailed file-by-file breakdown)

